snippet.title: PARANOIHELL - Teaser Trailer (Survival Horror Game)
snippet.description:
PARANOIHELL is chaotic nightmare about a woman who comes across something horrible during a late night walk home. Run, hide, fight back... whatever you choose, will you make it home alive? 

Highly influenced by PS2-era survival horror games, obscure Japanese horror games, and the films of David Lynch, and Dario Argento.

Coming later this year to itch.io
